Dr. Kathleen Lubey. Professor. B.A., Ithaca College. M.A., State University of New York at Buffalo. Ph.D., Rutgers University.
Kathleen Lubey is a Mellon Postdoctoral Fellow at the Penn Humanities Forum for 2008-09. She received her PhD in English from Rutgers University in 2005.
